params.sqlcmd: "SELECT " +" T_OD.OD_NO AS OD_NO, " +" T_OD.JOB_ODR_CD AS JOB_ODR_CD, " +" T_OD.JOB_ODR_DETAIL_NO AS JOB_ODR_DETAIL_NO, " +" T_OD.JOB_ODR_CANCEL_NO AS JOB_ODR_CANCEL_NO, " +" T_OD.ALC_GRP_CD AS ALC_GRP_CD, " +" TO_CHAR(NVL(T_OD.ODR_QTY, 0), 'FM999999999999999990.0999') AS ODR_QTY, " +" TO_CHAR(NVL(T_OD.DM_QTY, 0), 'FM999999999999999990.0999') AS DM_QTY, " +" M_ITEM.ITEM_NAME AS ITEM_NAME, " +" M_ITEM.UNIT_QTY_TYP AS UNIT_QTY_TYP, " +" M_ITEM.STOCK_UNIT AS STOCK_UNIT, " +" TO_CHAR(T_JOB_ODR.JOB_ODR_STS_TYP) AS JOB_ODR_STS_TYP, " +" T_OD.DM_STS_TYP AS DM_STS_TYP, " +" TO_CHAR(NVL(T_OD.TOTAL_ISSUE_QTY, 0), 'FM999999999999999990.0999') AS TOTAL_ISSUE_QTY, " +" TO_CHAR(T_OD.DUE_DATE, 'YYYY/MM/DD HH24:MI') AS DUE_DATE, " +" SYS_OD_CALC_CTRL.OD_CALC_FLG AS OD_CALC_FLG, " +" T_JOB_ODR.JOB_ODR_EXP_TYP AS JOB_ODR_EXP_TYP, " +" T_OD.MRP_TYP AS MRP_TYP, " +" T_OD.MRP_ODR_TYP AS MRP_ODR_TYP, " +" T_OD.PARENT_OD_NO AS PARENT_OD_NO, " +" T_OD.ITEM_CD AS ITEM_CD " +"FROM " +" T_OD, " +" M_ITEM, " +" T_JOB_ODR, " +" SYS_OD_CALC_CTRL " +"WHERE " +" T_OD.ITEM_CD = M_ITEM.ITEM_CD(+) " +" AND T_OD.JOB_ODR_CD = T_JOB_ODR.JOB_ODR_CD(+) " +" AND T_OD.JOB_ODR_DETAIL_NO = T_JOB_ODR.JOB_ODR_DETAIL_NO(+) " +" AND T_OD.JOB_ODR_CANCEL_NO = T_JOB_ODR.JOB_ODR_CANCEL_NO(+) " +" AND T_OD.PLANT_CD = SYS_OD_CALC_CTRL.PLANT_CD(+) " +" AND T_OD.PLANT_CD = T_JOB_ODR.PLANT_CD(+) " +" AND T_OD.PLANT_CD = ? " +" AND T_OD.JOB_ODR_CD = ? " +" AND T_OD.JOB_ODR_DETAIL_NO = ? " +" AND T_OD.JOB_ODR_CANCEL_NO = ? " +" AND T_OD.ITEM_CD = ? " +" AND T_OD.OD_NO = ?"

"SELECT " +" TO_CHAR(SUM(NVL(T_OD.ODR_QTY - T_OD.TOTAL_RCV_QTY, 0)), 'FM999999999999999990.0999') AS SUM_OF_WORK_IN_PROC_QTY " +"FROM " +" T_OD, " +" T_JOB_ODR " +"WHERE " +" T_OD.JOB_ODR_CD = T_JOB_ODR.JOB_ODR_CD(+) " +" AND T_OD.JOB_ODR_DETAIL_NO = T_JOB_ODR.JOB_ODR_DETAIL_NO(+) " +" AND T_OD.JOB_ODR_CANCEL_NO = T_JOB_ODR.JOB_ODR_CANCEL_NO(+) " +" AND T_OD.ITEM_CD = T_JOB_ODR.ITEM_CD(+) " +" AND T_OD.PARENT_OD_NO IS NULL " +" AND T_OD.JOB_ODR_CANCEL_NO = 0 " +" AND T_OD.ODR_STS_TYP <> 9 " +" AND T_JOB_ODR.JOB_ODR_TYP = 2 " +" AND T_OD.PLANT_CD = ? " +" AND T_OD.ITEM_CD = ? " +" AND T_OD.JOB_ODR_CD = ? " +" AND T_OD.JOB_ODR_DETAIL_NO = ? " +" AND T_OD.ODR_QTY > T_OD.TOTAL_RCV_QTY " +""

"SELECT " +" T_OD.OD_NO AS OD_NO, " +" TO_CHAR(NVL(T_OD.TOTAL_RCV_QTY, 0), 'FM999999999999999990.0999') AS TOTAL_RCV_QTY, " +" TO_CHAR(NVL(T_OD.TOTAL_ISSUE_QTY, 0), 'FM999999999999999990.0999') AS TOTAL_ISSUE_QTY " +"FROM " +" T_OD " +"WHERE " +" T_OD.PARENT_OD_NO IS NOT NULL " +" AND T_OD.DM_STS_TYP <> 9 " +" AND T_OD.PLANT_CD = ? " +" AND T_OD.ITEM_CD = ? " +" AND T_OD.JOB_ODR_CD = ? " +" AND T_OD.JOB_ODR_DETAIL_NO = ?"

"SELECT " +" T_OD.JOB_ODR_CD AS JOB_ODR_CD, " +" T_OD.JOB_ODR_DETAIL_NO AS JOB_ODR_DETAIL_NO, " +" T_OD.JOB_ODR_CANCEL_NO AS JOB_ODR_CANCEL_NO, " +" T_OD.ODR_STS_TYP AS ODR_STS_TYP, " +" FncGetFormattedDatetime(T_OD.PRD_DUE_DATE) AS PRD_DUE_DATE, " +" TO_CHAR(NVL(T_OD.TOTAL_RCV_QTY, 0), 'FM999999999999999990.0999') AS TOTAL_RCV_QTY, " +" FncGetFormattedDatetime(T_OD.ODR_START_DATE) AS ODR_START_DATE, " +" FncGetFormattedDatetime(T_OD.PRD_START_DATE) AS PRD_START_DATE, " +" TO_CHAR(NVL(T_OD.ODR_QTY, 0), 'FM999999999999999990.0999') AS ODR_QTY, " +" T_OD.ALC_GRP_CD AS ALC_GRP_CD, " +" TO_CHAR(T_JOB_ODR.JOB_ODR_STS_TYP) AS JOB_ODR_STS_TYP " +"FROM " +" T_OD, " +" T_JOB_ODR " +"WHERE " +" T_OD.PLANT_CD = ? " +" AND T_OD.JOB_ODR_CD = ? " +" AND T_OD.JOB_ODR_DETAIL_NO = ? " +" AND T_OD.ITEM_CD = ? " +" AND T_OD.PLANT_CD = T_JOB_ODR.PLANT_CD(+) " +" AND T_OD.JOB_ODR_CD = T_JOB_ODR.JOB_ODR_CD(+) " +" AND T_OD.JOB_ODR_DETAIL_NO = T_JOB_ODR.JOB_ODR_DETAIL_NO(+) " +" AND T_OD.ITEM_CD = T_JOB_ODR.ITEM_CD(+)"
"SELECT " +" SYS_OD_CALC_CTRL.OD_CALC_FLG AS OD_CALC_FLG, " +" SYS_OD_CALC_CTRL.OD_MNT_FLG AS OD_MNT_FLG " +"FROM " +" SYS_OD_CALC_CTRL " +"WHERE " +" SYS_OD_CALC_CTRL.PLANT_CD = ?"

"INSERT INTO " +" T_JOB_ODR_ALC(\\"JOB_ODR_ALC_CD\\", \\"OD_NO\\", \\"PLANT_CD\\", \\"ITEM_CD\\", \\"ALC_STOCK_TYP\\", \\"JOB_ODR_CD\\", \\"JOB_ODR_DETAIL_NO\\", \\"ALCD_QTY\\", \\"ISSUEED_QTY\\", \\"ISSUE_CMPLT_FLG\\") " +"VALUES " +" (?, ?, ?, ?, to_number(?), ?, to_number(?), to_number(?), to_number(?), to_number(?))"

"UPDATE " +" T_JOB_ODR_ALC " +"SET " +" ALCD_QTY = TO_NUMBER(?) " +"WHERE " +" OD_NO = ? " +" AND PLANT_CD = ? " +" AND JOB_ODR_CD = ? " +" AND JOB_ODR_DETAIL_NO = TO_NUMBER(?) " +" AND ALC_STOCK_TYP = TO_NUMBER(?)"

"DELETE FROM " +" T_JOB_ODR_ALC " +"WHERE " +" OD_NO = ? " +" AND PLANT_CD = ? " +" AND JOB_ODR_CD = ? " +" AND JOB_ODR_DETAIL_NO = TO_NUMBER(?) " +" AND ALC_STOCK_TYP = TO_NUMBER(?) " +" AND ISSUE_CMPLT_FLG = TO_NUMBER(?)"

"SELECT " +" T_OD.JOB_ODR_CD AS JOB_ODR_CD, " +" T_OD.JOB_ODR_DETAIL_NO AS JOB_ODR_DETAIL_NO, " +" T_OD.JOB_ODR_CANCEL_NO AS JOB_ODR_CANCEL_NO, " +" T_OD.ITEM_CD AS ITEM_CD, " +" T_OD.DM_STS_TYP AS DM_STS_TYP, " +" TO_CHAR(NVL(T_OD.ODR_QTY, 0), 'FM999999999999999990.0999') AS ODR_QTY, " +" TO_CHAR(NVL(T_OD.TOTAL_RCV_QTY, 0), 'FM999999999999999990.0999') AS TOTAL_RCV_QTY, " +" TO_CHAR(NVL(T_OD.ITEM_SPOIL, 0), 'FM999999999999999990.0999') AS ITEM_SPOIL, " +" TO_CHAR(NVL(T_OD.TOTAL_ISSUE_QTY, 0), 'FM999999999999999990.0999') AS TOTAL_ISSUE_QTY, " +" T_OD.ODR_STS_TYP AS ODR_STS_TYP, " +" T_OD.ALC_GRP_CD AS ALC_GRP_CD, " +" TO_CHAR(T_JOB_ODR.JOB_ODR_STS_TYP) AS JOB_ODR_STS_TYP, " +" FncGetFormattedDatetime(T_OD.PRD_DUE_DATE) AS PRD_DUE_DATE, " +" FncGetFormattedDatetime(T_OD.ODR_START_DATE) AS ODR_START_DATE, " +" FncGetFormattedDatetime(T_OD.PRD_START_DATE) AS PRD_START_DATE, " +" M_ITEM.UNIT_QTY_TYP AS UNIT_QTY_TYP, " +" T_OD.MRP_TYP AS MRP_TYP, " +" T_JOB_ODR.JOB_ODR_EXP_TYP AS JOB_ODR_EXP_TYP " +"FROM " +" T_OD, " +" T_JOB_ODR, " +" M_ITEM " +"WHERE " +" T_OD.PLANT_CD = ? " +" AND T_OD.OD_NO = ? " +" AND T_OD.JOB_ODR_CD = T_JOB_ODR.JOB_ODR_CD(+) " +" AND T_OD.JOB_ODR_DETAIL_NO = T_JOB_ODR.JOB_ODR_DETAIL_NO(+) " +" AND T_OD.JOB_ODR_CANCEL_NO = T_JOB_ODR.JOB_ODR_CANCEL_NO(+) " +" AND T_OD.ITEM_CD = M_ITEM.ITEM_CD(+)"

"SELECT " +" TO_CHAR(SUM(NVL(T_JOB_ODR_ALC.ISSUEED_QTY, 0)), 'FM999999999999999990.0999') AS SUM_OF_ISSUEED_QTY " +"FROM " +" T_JOB_ODR_ALC " +"WHERE " +" T_JOB_ODR_ALC.ISSUE_CMPLT_FLG = 0 " +" AND T_JOB_ODR_ALC.PLANT_CD = ? " +" AND T_JOB_ODR_ALC.OD_NO = ?"

"SELECT " +" MODIFY_COUNT, " +" TO_CHAR(NVL(ISSUEED_QTY, 0), 'FM999999999999999990.0999') AS ISSUEED_QTY " +"FROM " +" T_JOB_ODR_ALC " +"WHERE " +" OD_NO = ? " +" AND PLANT_CD = ? " +" AND ITEM_CD = ? " +" AND JOB_ODR_CD = ? " +" AND JOB_ODR_DETAIL_NO = ? " +" AND ALC_STOCK_TYP = ? " +" AND ISSUE_CMPLT_FLG = ?"
"DELETE FROM " +" T_JOB_ODR_ALC " +"WHERE " +" OD_NO = ? " +" AND PLANT_CD = ? " +" AND ALC_STOCK_TYP = TO_NUMBER(?) " +" AND ISSUE_CMPLT_FLG = TO_NUMBER(?)"
"UPDATE " +" T_JOB_ODR_ALC " +"SET " +" ALCD_QTY = TO_NUMBER(?) " +"WHERE " +" OD_NO = ? " +" AND PLANT_CD = ? " +" AND ALC_STOCK_TYP = TO_NUMBER(?)"
"SELECT " +" JOB_ODR_EXP_TYP " +"FROM " +" T_JOB_ODR " +"WHERE " +" PLANT_CD = ? " +" AND JOB_ODR_CD = ? " +" AND JOB_ODR_DETAIL_NO = ? " +" AND JOB_ODR_CANCEL_NO = ?"
"SELECT " +" MRP_ODR_TYP, " +" UNIT_QTY_TYP " +"FROM " +" M_ITEM " +"WHERE " +" ITEM_CD = ?"

"SELECT DISTINCT " +" o.OD_NO AS OD_NO, " +" o.JOB_ODR_CD AS JOB_ODR_CD, " +" o.JOB_ODR_DETAIL_NO AS JOB_ODR_DETAIL_NO, " +" o.JOB_ODR_CANCEL_NO AS JOB_ODR_CANCEL_NO, " +" o.PARENT_OD_NO AS PARENT_OD_NO, " +" o.ALC_GRP_CD AS ALC_GRP_CD, " +" o.ODR_STS_TYP AS ODR_STS_TYP, " +" o.DM_STS_TYP AS DM_STS_TYP, " +" j.JOB_ODR_TYP AS JOB_ODR_TYP, " +" TO_CHAR(j.JOB_ODR_STS_TYP) AS JOB_ODR_STS_TYP, " +" TO_CHAR(NVL(o.TOTAL_RCV_QTY, 0), 'FM999999999999999990.0999') AS TOTAL_RCV_QTY, " +" TO_CHAR(NVL(o.ODR_QTY, 0), 'FM999999999999999990.0999') AS ODR_QTY, " +" FncGetFormattedDatetime(o.PRD_DUE_DATE) AS PRD_DUE_DATE, " +" FncGetFormattedDatetime(o.ODR_START_DATE) AS ODR_START_DATE, " +" FncGetFormattedDatetime(o.PRD_START_DATE) AS PRD_START_DATE, " +" TO_CHAR(NVL(o.ITEM_SPOIL, 0), 'FM999999999999999990.0999') AS ITEM_SPOIL " +"FROM " +" T_OD o, " +" T_JOB_ODR j " +"WHERE " +" o.JOB_ODR_CD = j.JOB_ODR_CD(+) " +" AND o.JOB_ODR_DETAIL_NO = j.JOB_ODR_DETAIL_NO(+) " +" AND o.JOB_ODR_CANCEL_NO = j.JOB_ODR_CANCEL_NO(+) " +" AND o.ITEM_CD = ? " +" AND o.PLANT_CD = ? " +" AND NOT EXISTS( " +" SELECT " +" JOB_ODR_CD " +" FROM " +" T_JOB_ODR_ALC " +" WHERE " +" PLANT_CD = O.PLANT_CD " +" AND JOB_ODR_CD = O.JOB_ODR_CD " +" AND JOB_ODR_DETAIL_NO = O.JOB_ODR_DETAIL_NO " +" AND OD_NO = ? " +" AND ISSUE_CMPLT_FLG = 0 " +" ) " +" AND O.OD_NO <> ? " +"ORDER BY " +" FncGetFormattedDatetime(o.PRD_DUE_DATE), " +" o.JOB_ODR_CD"

"SELECT " +" TO_CHAR(NVL(T_JOB_ODR_ALC.ALCD_QTY, 0), 'FM999999999999999990.0999') AS ALCD_QTY, " +" TO_CHAR(NVL(T_JOB_ODR_ALC.ISSUEED_QTY, 0), 'FM999999999999999990.0999') AS ISSUEED_QTY, " +" TO_CHAR((NVL(T_JOB_ODR_ALC.ALCD_QTY, 0) - NVL(T_JOB_ODR_ALC.ISSUEED_QTY, 0)), 'FM999999999999999990.0999') AS ISSUE_REMAIN_QTY, " +" T_JOB_ODR_ALC.MODIFY_COUNT AS MODIFY_COUNT, " +" T_JOB_ODR.JOB_ODR_EXP_TYP AS JOB_ODR_EXP_TYP, " +" T_OD.MRP_TYP AS MRP_TYP, " +" T_OD.ITEM_CD AS ITEM_CD " +"FROM " +" T_JOB_ODR_ALC, " +" T_JOB_ODR, " +" T_OD " +"WHERE " +" T_JOB_ODR_ALC.ALC_STOCK_TYP = 1 " +" AND T_JOB_ODR_ALC.PLANT_CD = ? " +" AND T_JOB_ODR_ALC.OD_NO = ? " +" AND T_JOB_ODR_ALC.JOB_ODR_CD = T_JOB_ODR.JOB_ODR_CD(+) " +" AND T_JOB_ODR_ALC.JOB_ODR_DETAIL_NO = T_JOB_ODR.JOB_ODR_DETAIL_NO(+) " +" AND T_JOB_ODR.JOB_ODR_CANCEL_NO(+) = 0 " +" AND T_JOB_ODR_ALC.OD_NO = T_OD.OD_NO(+)"

"SELECT " +" T_JOB_ODR_ALC.JOB_ODR_CD AS JOB_ODR_CD, " +" T_JOB_ODR_ALC.JOB_ODR_DETAIL_NO AS JOB_ODR_DETAIL_NO, " +" TO_CHAR(NVL(T_JOB_ODR_ALC.ALCD_QTY, 0), 'FM999999999999999990.0999') AS ALCD_QTY, " +" TO_CHAR(NVL(T_JOB_ODR_ALC.ISSUEED_QTY, 0), 'FM999999999999999990.0999') AS ISSUEED_QTY, " +" TO_CHAR((NVL(T_JOB_ODR_ALC.ALCD_QTY, 0) - NVL(T_JOB_ODR_ALC.ISSUEED_QTY, 0)), 'FM999999999999999990.0999') AS ISSUE_REMAIN_QTY, " +" T_OD.ODR_STS_TYP AS ODR_STS_TYP, " +" FncGetFormattedDatetime(T_OD.PRD_DUE_DATE) AS PRD_DUE_DATE, " +" TO_CHAR(NVL(T_OD.TOTAL_RCV_QTY, 0), 'FM999999999999999990.0999') AS TOTAL_RCV_QTY, " +" FncGetFormattedDatetime(T_OD.ODR_START_DATE) AS ODR_START_DATE, " +" FncGetFormattedDatetime(T_OD.PRD_START_DATE) AS PRD_START_DATE, " +" T_JOB_ODR_ALC.MODIFY_COUNT AS MODIFY_COUNT, " +" T_OD.MRP_TYP AS MRP_TYP, " +" T_JOB_ODR.JOB_ODR_EXP_TYP AS JOB_ODR_EXP_TYP, " +" T_OD.ITEM_CD AS ITEM_CD " +"FROM " +" T_JOB_ODR_ALC, " +" T_JOB_ODR, " +" T_OD " +"WHERE " +" T_JOB_ODR_ALC.OD_NO = T_OD.OD_NO(+) " +" AND T_JOB_ODR_ALC.ALC_STOCK_TYP = 2 " +" AND T_JOB_ODR_ALC.ISSUE_CMPLT_FLG = 0 " +" AND T_JOB_ODR_ALC.PLANT_CD = ? " +" AND T_JOB_ODR_ALC.OD_NO = ? " +" AND T_JOB_ODR_ALC.JOB_ODR_CD = T_JOB_ODR.JOB_ODR_CD(+) " +" AND T_JOB_ODR_ALC.JOB_ODR_DETAIL_NO = T_JOB_ODR.JOB_ODR_DETAIL_NO(+) " +" AND T_JOB_ODR.JOB_ODR_CANCEL_NO(+) = 0 " +"ORDER BY " +" TO_CHAR(T_OD.PRD_DUE_DATE,'YYYY/MM/DD HH24:MI'), " +" T_JOB_ODR_ALC.JOB_ODR_CD"

"SELECT " +" TO_CHAR(NVL(ALCD_QTY, 0), 'FM999999999999999990.0999') AS ALCD_QTY " +"FROM " +" T_JOB_ODR_ALC " +"WHERE " +" OD_NO = ? " +" AND PLANT_CD = ? " +" AND JOB_ODR_CD = ? " +" AND JOB_ODR_DETAIL_NO = ? " +" AND ALC_STOCK_TYP = ? " +" AND ISSUE_CMPLT_FLG = ?"
"SELECT " +" MRP_TYP " +"FROM " +" T_OD " +"WHERE " +" OD_NO = ?"
"UPDATE " +" T_OD " +"SET " +" \\"OD_GNR_TYP\\" = ? " +"WHERE " +" OD_NO = ? " +" AND PLANT_CD = ?"

"SELECT " +" TO_CHAR(SUM(NVL(T_JOB_ODR_ALC.ISSUEED_QTY, 0)), 'FM999999999999999990.0999') AS SUM_OF_ISSUED_QTY " +"FROM " +" T_JOB_ODR_ALC " +"WHERE " +" T_JOB_ODR_ALC.ISSUE_CMPLT_FLG = 0 " +" AND T_JOB_ODR_ALC.PLANT_CD = ? " +" AND T_JOB_ODR_ALC.OD_NO = ? " +" AND T_JOB_ODR_ALC.ITEM_CD = ? " +"GROUP BY " +" T_JOB_ODR_ALC.OD_NO"

"SELECT " +" TO_CHAR(SUM(NVL(T_ITEM_STOCK.STOCK_ON_HAND_QTY, 0)), 'FM999999999999999990.0999') AS SUM_OF_STOCK_ON_HAND_QTY " +"FROM " +" T_ITEM_STOCK, " +" M_WH " +"WHERE " +" T_ITEM_STOCK.WH_CD = M_WH.WH_CD(+) " +" AND M_WH.MRP_FLG = 1 " +" AND T_ITEM_STOCK.PLANT_CD = ? " +" AND T_ITEM_STOCK.ITEM_CD = ? " +"GROUP BY " +" T_ITEM_STOCK.PLANT_CD, " +" T_ITEM_STOCK.ITEM_CD"

"SELECT " +" TO_CHAR(SUM(NVL(T_JOB_ODR_CD_STOCK.STOCK_ON_HAND_QTY, 0)), 'FM999999999999999990.0999') AS SUM_OF_STOCK_ON_HAND_QTY " +"FROM " +" T_JOB_ODR_CD_STOCK, " +" M_WH " +"WHERE " +" T_JOB_ODR_CD_STOCK.WH_CD = M_WH.WH_CD(+) " +" AND M_WH.MRP_FLG = 1 " +" AND T_JOB_ODR_CD_STOCK.PLANT_CD = ? " +" AND T_JOB_ODR_CD_STOCK.ITEM_CD = ? " +" AND T_JOB_ODR_CD_STOCK.JOB_ODR_CD = ? " +" AND T_JOB_ODR_CD_STOCK.JOB_ODR_DETAIL_NO = ?"

"SELECT " +" TO_CHAR(SUM(NVL(T_JOB_ODR_ALC.ALCD_QTY, 0) - NVL(T_JOB_ODR_ALC.ISSUEED_QTY, 0)), 'FM999999999999999990.0999') AS SUM_OF_ALCD_QTY " +"FROM " +" T_JOB_ODR_ALC " +"WHERE " +" T_JOB_ODR_ALC.ALC_STOCK_TYP = 2 " +" AND T_JOB_ODR_ALC.ISSUE_CMPLT_FLG = 0 " +" AND T_JOB_ODR_ALC.PLANT_CD = ? " +" AND T_JOB_ODR_ALC.ITEM_CD = ? " +" AND T_JOB_ODR_ALC.JOB_ODR_CD = ? " +" AND T_JOB_ODR_ALC.JOB_ODR_DETAIL_NO = ?"

"SELECT " +" TO_CHAR(SUM(NVL(T_JOB_ODR_ALC.ALCD_QTY, 0) - NVL(T_JOB_ODR_ALC.ISSUEED_QTY, 0)), 'FM999999999999999990.0999') AS SUM_OF_ALCD_QTY " +"FROM " +" T_JOB_ODR_ALC " +"WHERE " +" T_JOB_ODR_ALC.ALC_STOCK_TYP = 1 " +" AND T_JOB_ODR_ALC.ISSUE_CMPLT_FLG = 0 " +" AND T_JOB_ODR_ALC.PLANT_CD = ? " +" AND T_JOB_ODR_ALC.ITEM_CD = ? " +"GROUP BY " +" T_JOB_ODR_ALC.PLANT_CD, " +" T_JOB_ODR_ALC.ITEM_CD"

"SELECT " +" SUM(SYS_JOB_OD_CALC_CTRL.OD_CALC_FLG) AS OD_CALC_FLG, " +" SUM(SYS_JOB_OD_CALC_CTRL.OD_MNT_FLG) AS OD_MNT_FLG " +"FROM " +" SYS_JOB_OD_CALC_CTRL " +"WHERE " +" SYS_JOB_OD_CALC_CTRL.PLANT_CD = ? " +" AND(SYS_JOB_OD_CALC_CTRL.JOB_ODR_CD = ? " +" OR SYS_JOB_OD_CALC_CTRL.JOB_ODR_CD = ?) " +"GROUP BY SYS_JOB_OD_CALC_CTRL.PLANT_CD"
"SELECT " +" OD_NO " +"FROM " +" T_OD " +"WHERE " +" OD_NO = ? " +" AND PLANT_CD = ? " +"FOR UPDATE NOWAIT"
